WEBVTT

00:00.213 --> 00:01.579
My name
is Michael Westen.

00:01.631 --> 00:03.682
I used to be
a spy until...

00:03.749 --> 00:05.466
We got a burn notice on you.

00:05.501 --> 00:07.335
You're blacklisted.

00:07.386 --> 00:09.754
When you're burned,
you've got nothing--

00:09.839 --> 00:12.007
no cash, no credit,
no job history.

00:12.058 --> 00:14.375
You're stuck in whatever city
they decide to dump you in.

00:14.427 --> 00:16.761
- Where am I?
- Miami.

00:16.846 --> 00:19.097
You do whatever work
comes your way.

00:19.181 --> 00:21.266
You rely on anyone
who's still talking to you...

00:22.768 --> 00:23.735
A trigger-happy girlfriend...

00:23.819 --> 00:25.186
Should we shoot them?

00:25.237 --> 00:27.188
An old friend who used
to inform on you to the FBI...

00:27.239 --> 00:29.824
You know spies--
bunch of bitchy little girls.

00:29.892 --> 00:31.225
Family too...

00:31.277 --> 00:32.159
Hey, is that your mom again?

00:32.226 --> 00:33.328
If you're desperate...

00:33.395 --> 00:34.675
Someone needs your help,
Michael.

00:34.697 --> 00:37.365
And a down-and-out spy
you met along the way.

00:37.416 --> 00:38.917
That's how we do it,
people.

00:39.001 --> 00:41.670
Bottom line,
as long as you're burned,

00:41.737 --> 00:44.706
you're not going anywhere.

00:45.317 --> 00:46.384
It's a deep-cover job.

00:46.385 --> 00:48.336
We're going after the leader
of a terrorist network.

00:48.420 --> 00:50.671
I need you to bring them down
no matter what.

00:50.756 --> 00:52.590
I'm a man who's willing
to go extremes

00:52.641 --> 00:54.292
to do what I feel is right.

00:54.359 --> 00:55.560
This guy James,
he's getting to you.

00:55.627 --> 00:57.895
They all are.

00:57.963 --> 01:00.515
I'm working with the CIA.

01:00.599 --> 01:03.067
I gave up everything,
even after they burned me,

01:03.135 --> 01:05.203
and I wasted my life.

01:05.269 --> 01:07.939
- You have to turn me in.
- What? No.

01:07.990 --> 01:09.690
Our work will continue.

01:09.775 --> 01:11.692
How will it continue
without a leader?

01:11.777 --> 01:15.029
I see two leaders standing
right before me.

01:15.114 --> 01:16.480
Michael, where are you?

01:16.532 --> 01:18.032
James is coming to Miami.

01:18.117 --> 01:19.617
Get your team ready.

01:19.668 --> 01:23.337
Wait a minute.

01:23.422 --> 01:26.124
- Son of a bitch.
- Mike switched sides.

01:30.179 --> 01:32.997
You stay the hell out
of my way, Sam.

01:35.100 --> 01:36.500
Fi...

01:36.552 --> 01:38.436
I thought you said
she wouldn't be a problem.

01:38.503 --> 01:39.887
I just need
to figure this out.

01:39.972 --> 01:41.105
There's nothing
to figure out, Michael.

01:41.173 --> 01:42.607
James is here.
I'll figure this out.

01:42.674 --> 01:44.308
The CIA is closing in.

01:44.359 --> 01:46.227
We have to finish this now.

01:46.311 --> 01:48.345
If you won't do it,
I will.

01:52.551 --> 01:55.486
Every spy lives in fear
of losing himself.

01:55.537 --> 01:56.854
The CIA is closing in.

01:56.905 --> 01:58.873
We have to finish this now.

01:58.957 --> 02:00.625
Do what you think
is right.

02:00.692 --> 02:01.993
When you work undercover,

02:02.044 --> 02:04.495
the lines between loyalty
and betrayal

02:04.546 --> 02:07.031
can become so blurred,
so grey,

02:07.082 --> 02:09.000
that after a while
you don't know

02:09.050 --> 02:11.169
what you're fighting for
anymore.

02:11.220 --> 02:13.638
Michael, think of all the good
things we could do together.

02:13.705 --> 02:14.972
You end up caught
in the middle

02:15.040 --> 02:16.641
as your friends become
your enemies

02:16.708 --> 02:18.843
and your enemies become
your friends.

02:18.894 --> 02:21.312
If this is what you want,
the man I love is gone.

02:21.379 --> 02:23.097
If you won't do it, I will.

02:23.182 --> 02:25.266
The man I love is gone.

02:25.350 --> 02:29.053
Until the time comes when
you're forced to make a choice.

